### Formatting

Advanced text formatting and change tracking:

```markdown
==highlighted text==
^^inserted text^^
~~deleted text~~
H~2~O (subscript)
A^T^A (superscript)
++ctrl+alt+del++ (keyboard keys)
```

**Critic Markup** (change tracking):

```markdown
{--deleted text--}
{++added text++}
{~~old~>new~~}
{==highlighted==}
{>>comment<<}
```

